                    "image": "Sidebar_4_RelatedCreatures.png"
                },
                "html": "On the rare occasions that cloakers associate with other creatures, they tend to ally with those <a aonid=\"3\" game-obj=\"Monsters\">ulat\u2011kinis</a> who are no longer the thralls of the alghollthus and, rarely, with <a aonid=\"107\" game-obj=\"Monsters\">deros</a>, though they consider the latter irrational and untrustworthy. Cloakers never willingly associate with alghollthus."
            },
